notifications.title: New Version Available
notifications.message: CTA Manager v2.1.0 is now available with performance improvements and new features.

notifications.title: Performance Tip
notifications.message: Enable 'Load Scripts in Footer' in Settings for faster page loads.

notifications.title: Did You Know?
notifications.message: You can schedule CTAs to appear only during specific date ranges using the scheduling feature.

notifications.title: Milestone Reached!
notifications.message: Your CTAs have received over 1,000 total impressions. View your analytics to see top performers.

notifications.title: Weekly Performance Summary
notifications.message: This week: 523 impressions, 47 clicks (9.0% CTR). Your top CTA is 'Contact Sales'.

notifications.title: Getting Started Guide
notifications.message: New to CTA Manager? Check out our quick start guide to create your first call-to-action.

notifications.title: Backup Reminder
notifications.message: It's been 30 days since your last export. Consider backing up your CTAs and settings.

notifications.title: Unlock Advanced Analytics
notifications.message: Pro users get detailed event logs, custom retention periods, and CSV/JSON exports.

notifications.title: Mobile Optimization
notifications.message: 85% of your traffic is mobile. Consider using mobile-optimized layouts for better engagement.

notifications.title: Seasonal Campaign Ideas
notifications.message: Boost conversions with holiday-themed CTAs. Enable scheduling to auto-activate seasonal promotions.

notifications.title: Quick Tip
notifications.message: CTAs with clear call-to-action text typically convert 2x better than generic buttons.

notifications.title: A/B Test Complete
notifications.message: Your 'Holiday Promo' experiment has concluded. Variant B performed 23% better.

notifications.title: Complete Your Setup
notifications.message: Your CTA is missing required fields. Complete the form to publish.

notifications.title: System Maintenance
notifications.message: Scheduled maintenance window: Saturday 2am-4am UTC. Analytics collection will be paused.
